data.description: Welcome to your new Dream Home in the highly desired Turning Stone Subdivision. This luxurious and spacious one-story home offers plenty of open space with 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and an office suite. Throughout your new home, you will notice high tray ceilings, custom lighting, custom ceramic tile and engineered wood flooring. Plus, many features to cater for all indoor and outdoor occasions for family and friends with a gourmet customized kitchen with quartz countertops, double ovens, custom backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and attractive decorative brick. The backyard is a private oasis with a 21 x 15 outdoor patio and kitchen with pergola and a shed for extra storage. Your beautiful Dream Home awaits you for the holidays.
